title: Personalized Apartment List - Austin Apartment Locating Service
posting_body: ['I am a licensed Realtor® and Apartment Locator, and would love to help you find your next home.', 'As your advocate, my priority is to provide exceptional service and guide you in the search for the perfect place.', 'As a Realtor®, I am bound by a strict code of ethics and laws that are in place to protect you.', 'Confidentiality is a big part of that.', 'I am paid for my time, work and services by the apartment community when you list me as your referral source on your application and guest card and move into your home.', "Whether you're looking to lease a apartment, condo, townhome, high-rise, mid-rise, luxury apartment, or a Penthouse Suite, I can help!", 'I have access to multiple databases.', 'I will just need the following from you to get started:', '1.', 'First and Last Name(s)', '2.', 'E-mail(s)', '3.', 'Phone #(s)', '4.', 'Preferred Move-In Date', '5.', 'Desired Location', '6.', 'Price Range', 'Thank you for choosing Core One Real Estate.', 'I look forward to working with you!', 'Minimum credit score of 550 is required.', '#austin', '#apartments', '#relocation', '#soco', '#bartonsprings', '#atx', '#specials', '#realtor', '#realestate']
